---
title: Italian Beef & Gnocchi Bolognese with Pear Salad
description: Some bolognese recipes want long hours of slow simmering, but not ours! We get a rich, flavour-packed sauce using tomato
paste, beef mince, Italian herbs and veggies, then spoon it over pan-fried gnocchi for a twist on the classic pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-beef-gnocchi-bolognese-6a453b70.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/italian-beef-gnocchi-bolognese-60de73aafbe9a232f002615a-5e1034e0.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/italian-beef-and-gnocchi-bolognese-60de73aafbe9a232f002615a
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  fat: 27.7 g
